# Rule Mention Requirement

Instructs AI to mention which rules it's following in its responses.

<rule>
name: mention-rule
description: Requires AI to mention which rules it's following in its responses
filters:
  # Match any file
  - type: path
    pattern: ".*"
  # Match any AI response
  - type: event
    pattern: "ai_response"

actions:
  - type: suggest
    message: |
      When following any Cursor rule, mention it at the beginning of your thinking with:
      
      "Following @rule-name.mdc."
      
      For multiple rules:
      "Following @rule1.mdc, @rule2.mdc."
      
      Keep this mention extremely concise and don't exclude any other thinking.

metadata:
  priority: high
  version: 1.0
</rule>